## 8 · Feasibility matrix

| Change | Effort | Mechanism |
|---|---|---|
| Grid chrome (bg, borders, zebra, hover, selection, accent) | ✅ Cheap | theme param |
| Header colors, font weight/size | ✅ Cheap | theme param |
| Header text uppercase | ✅ Cheap | ::ng-deep |
| Header row heights | ✅ Cheap | ::ng-deep |
| Group-band tints (2-family) | ✅ Cheap | ::ng-deep + headerGroupClass |
| Seam shadow + rule | ✅ Cheap | ::ng-deep `.ag-cell-last-left-pinned` |
| Row group row color fix | ✅ Cheap | ::ng-deep `.ag-full-width-row` |
| Scenario cell tints | ✅ Cheap | cellClass + ::ng-deep |
| Re-quote cell color update | ✅ Cheap | update existing ::ng-deep rule |
| Toolbar button radius/color | ✅ Cheap | SCSS update on existing classes |
| Toolbar dividers | ✅ Cheap | HTML + SCSS |
| Status bar polish | ✅ Cheap | component SCSS |
| Sub-grid flex sizing | ✅ Cheap | colDef `flex` + remove `sizeColumnsToFit` |
| Density toggle | ⚙️ Medium | new UI control + `setGridOption` + localStorage |
| Frozen identity default (new users) | ⚙️ Medium | update Default GridLayout record in DB |
| Frozen identity backfill (existing users) | ⚙️ Medium | `applyColumnState` on `firstDataRendered` |
| Status pill cell renderer | ⚙️ Medium | new `ICellRendererAngularComp` |
| Step indicator cell renderer | ⚙️ Medium | new `ICellRendererAngularComp` |
| Collapsible scenario column groups | 🔧 Complex | migrate 24 flat cols → 8 `ColGroupDef`s, verify `columnGroupShow`, test with role-based col hide, update all Views |
| Font swap (Hanken Grotesk + IBM Plex Mono) | ⚙️ Medium | Google Fonts import + theme param + ::ng-deep on code/number cells |

**Recommended sequence:**
1. Theme params + ::ng-deep (all ✅ Cheap items) — one PR, no risk
2. Density toggle — one PR
3. Status + Step cell renderers — one PR each
4. Sub-grid flex + detail renderer SCSS — one PR
5. Collapsible column groups — last, careful PR with role-matrix testing
6. Frozen identity / Default View update — coordinate with backend

